<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">

    <title>Product Review Platform - Start Reviewing</title>

    <!-- Nav Bar CSS -->
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "bootstrap.min", :media => "all" %>

    <!-- Custom fonts for this template -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Catamaran:100,200,300,400,500,600,700,800,900" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,100i,300,300i,400,400i,700,700i,900,900i" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Custom styles for this template -->
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "one-page-wonder.min", :media => "all" %>

    <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript -->
    <%= javascript_include_tag "jquery.min" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "bootstrap.bundle.min" %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%= render 'layouts/header' %>

    <header class="masthead text-center text-white">
      <div class="masthead-content">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="masthead-heading mb-0">Find the Best Business</h1>
          <h2 class="masthead-heading mb-0">Partners and Vendors</h2>
          <a href="#main" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl rounded-pill mt-5">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-circle-1 bg-circle"></div>
      <div class="bg-circle-2 bg-circle"></div>
      <div class="bg-circle-3 bg-circle"></div>
      <div class="bg-circle-4 bg-circle"></div>
    </header>

    <section id="main">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
            <div class="p-5">
              <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="/assets/01.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
            <div class="p-5">
              <h2 class="display-4">Crowdsourcing of Reviews</h2>
              <p>Businesses can leave reviews and ratings for consultants that
              they have previously engaged for their projects, to develop a
             source of authentic, honest and helpful feedback that is direct
           from the market.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="p-5">
              <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="/assets/02.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="p-5">
              <h2 class="display-4">Leave feedback to help others</h2>
              <p>Businesses do not know which consultant to engage for their
              grant projects. Evaluating officers spend a sizable amount of
            time and effort to assess the background of consultants. These
          feedbacks will reduce the time and effort for businesses and evaluating officers, thus improve their productivity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
            <div class="p-5">
              <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="/assets/03.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
            <div class="p-5">
              <h2 class="display-4">Ease of Integration</h2>
              <p>The platform is built with API-centricity in mind using modern
              RESTful API. Developers can use the API docs and playground
            to test and develop their applications or visualisation
          dashboards with their own customizations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="py-5 bg-black">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="m-0 text-center text-white small">Copyright &copy; GovTech 2018</p>
      </div>
      <!-- /.container -->
    </footer>
  </body>

</html>
